lac.cnet.sddl.udi.core

Interface DDSLayer

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CoreDXLayer

    public interface DDSLayer
    All DDS Access Layers should implement this Interface. The DDSLayer permits a (almost) uniform access to different DDS vendors.
    Author:
    Rafael Oliveira Vasconcelos
